<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0007', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:196'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='196:211'>　毛詩指説　　　　　　詩類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='211:217'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='217:244'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案毛詩指説一卷唐成伯璵撰伯璵爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='244:267'>　　　　里無考書凡四篇一曰興述明先王陳詩觀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='267:290'>　　　　風之㫖孔子刪詩正雅之由二曰解説先釋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='290:313'>　　　　詩義而風雅頌次之周又次之詁傳序又次</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='313:336'>　　　　之篇章又次之后妃又次之終之以鵲巢騶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='336:362'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0007', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='362:392'>　　　　虞大畧即舉周南一篇<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1357' title='KR1357' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1357.png'/>括論列引申以及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='392:415'>　　　　其餘三曰傳受備詳齊魯毛韓四家授受世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='415:438'>　　　　次及後儒訓釋源流四曰文體凡三百篇中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='438:461'>　　　　句法之長短篇章之多寡措辭之異同用字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='461:484'>　　　　之體例皆臚舉而詳之頗似劉氏文心雕龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='484:507'>　　　　之體葢説經之餘論也然定詩序首句為子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='507:531'>　　　　夏所傳其下為毛萇所續實伯璵此書𤼵其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='531:554'>　　　　端則決别疑似於説詩亦深有功矣伯璵尚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='554:580'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0007', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='580:603'>　　　　有毛詩斷章二卷見崇文總目稱其取春秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='603:626'>　　　　斷章之義抄取詩語彚而出之葢即李石詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='626:650'>　　　　如例之𩔖宋熊克嘗與毘陵沈少豫欲合二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='650:674'>　　　　書刻之而斷章一書竟求之不𫉬乃先刻指</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='674:697'>　　　　説此本末有克跋葢即從宋本傳刻也克嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='697:721'>　　　　著中興小厯别見史部編年𩔖中其刻此書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='721:744'>　　　　時方分教於京口故跋稱刻之泮林云乾隆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='744:759'>　　　　四十六年三月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='759:785'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0007', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
